### Guide to create label file
> 1. Choose source image folder
> 2. Choose folder to store label file
> 3. Tick the textbox to auto replace all absolute path or relative path between source folder and label folder.
* Note: the label file name will be stored as source image folder.


### Important shortcuts

* `<Arrow-Left>` to go to previous image. It will go to last image if the cursor is at first image.
* `<Arrow-Left>` to go to next image. It will go to first image if the cursor is at last image
* `<Enter>` to save ground true text label
* `<ESC>` to exit the program

